@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Endgames";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p><strong>Importance:</strong> ★★★★☆</p>

<h2>What it includes</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Basic mates (K+Q vs K, K+R vs K)</li>
    <li>Key theoretical positions (Lucena, Philidor, opposition, triangulation)</li>
    <li>Technique in simplified positions</li>
    <li>Understanding of pawn endgames and conversion methods</li>
</ul>

<h2>Why it matters</h2>
<p>
    Endgames reveal the player’s technique. Even small advantages often require exact knowledge to convert, and many winning middlegames fail without endgame mastery.
</p>
